    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has started to soften, add the <strong>arborio rice</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> to the<strong> </strong>pan stirring to coat the grains of rice in the oil</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and stir continuously until the rice has absorbed most of the tomato juice</p>",
