    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all the stock has absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>tomato risotto</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
