    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grind<strong> </strong>most<strong> </strong>of the <strong>chopped basil</strong> (save some for garnish!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> to form a paste</p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and mix well – this is your <strong>basil oil</strong></p><p>Tip: If you don't have a pestle & mortar, chop the basil leaves very finely and mix with olive oil</p>",
